HEADWORD: Fairness
<hw>Fair"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state of being fair, or free
form spots or stains, as of the skin; honesty, as of dealing; candor, as
of an argument, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fair-spoken</ent>⟦br⟧
